{"tid":1173557,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"傳中共軍機秦嶺墜毀 6名軍人全部身亡","createTime":"2019-05-27T08:00:04.000Z","updateTime":"2019-05-27T11:58:55.000Z","uid":184679,"like":25,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"819228b08ad86196f877a73fefc6263d07e70bd6","tid":1173557,"uid":184679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-27T08:00:04.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img2.secretchina.com/pic/2019/5-27/p2432341a825728636-ss.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg2.secretchina.com%2Fpic%2F2019%2F5-27%2Fp2432341a825728636-ss.jpg&h=da8218d5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n（微博圖片）<br />\n<br />\n近期頻繁傳出中共軍機墜毀事件。日前中共軍改新增的西藏軍區陸航旅一架直升機墜毀，造成6名現役軍人全部死亡。<br />\n<br />\n5月27日，一組「921721機組烈士永垂不朽」照片在網路流傳，照片中出現6名現役軍人的遺像。根據中共軍機編號規則，「921721機」是一架隸屬於西藏軍區的陸航旅的米-17系列運輸直升機。<br />\n<br />\n網路上沒有給出這組照片的具體信息，中共媒體也沒有提及6名現役軍人死亡的消息。<br />\n<br />\n不過，陸媒25日消息稱，一名叫房浩的現役軍人在13日執行飛行任務時，途徑漢中秦嶺時不幸墜機死亡。房浩生前是一名西藏軍區的軍人，曾在新疆軍區陸航旅服役，由一名陸航機務轉為陸航無線電技師。<br />\n<br />\n媒體據此推斷，「921721」機組駕駛的直升機應是在5月13日在秦嶺上空墜毀的，導致包括房浩在內的6人全部死亡。<br />\n<br />\n在中共最新一輪軍改後，西藏軍區增設陸航旅部隊，屬於一支新的部隊，裝備也多從其他部隊轉隸，包括俄制米-171運輸直升機。 <br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.secretchina.com/news/b5/2019/05/27/894955.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.secretchina.com%2Fnews%2Fb5%2F2019%2F05%2F27%2F894955.html&d=I3HUAc%2BVzuGSjYFa2O0dWKNZBGycwMyv8OGD44uLuTw%3D&h=06d4dc49\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.secretchina.com/news/b5/2019/05/27/894955.html</a>"},{"pid":"04bb889eb9dc7aa9261ce32e257bbc4ff91d848f","tid":1173557,"uid":172465,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-27T08:12:15.000Z","msg":"喜獲毛主席接見<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"aed60f8619bed404e5cd66581c68f9f2b77b4fe0","tid":1173557,"uid":226955,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-27T08:13:16.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"623f99371b2e67f43ed7291b2fc74cf0e5250b5f","tid":1173557,"uid":105387,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-27T08:26:41.000Z","msg":"沒事兒"},{"pid":"240b6438ed25ce428287e11c5a2d2007bb0bcd5e","tid":1173557,"uid":94454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-27T08:27:21.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ecbcdf78ae48664a8a25a04d2b7cf40ab40dbc44","tid":1173557,"uid":184679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-27T11:58:55.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}